</m:mrow>
</m:mfrac>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-22">
Now, the force on the projectile of mass "m" is due to the force of gravity :
</para>
<para id="element-23">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
